            <div class="card-body">
              <h2 class="card-title mx-3 mt-5" style="font-weight:bold">Education</h2>
              <p class="card-text mx-3" style="font-size:25px;">
                <br><a href="http://cse.koreatech.ac.kr" style="color:black; text-decoration:underline;">한국기술교육대학교</a> 컴퓨터공학부 (2010 ~ 2017)
