              <p class="card-text mx-3" style="font-size:25px;">
                <br><a style="color:black; text-decoration:underline;">창업동아리 메이커스</a> (2016.12 ~ 2017.09)
                <br><a href="https://lora.sktiot.com/contest" style="color:black; text-decoration:underline;">SKT 메이커톤</a> (2016.08)
                <br><a href="https://uni.likelion.org/hackton" style="color:black; text-decoration:underline;">멋쟁이사자처럼 해커톤</a> (2017.09)
                <br>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Pages -->
            <div class="card-body">
              <h2 class="card-title mx-3 mt-5" style="font-weight:bold">Pages</h2>
              <p class="card-text mx-3 mb-5" style="font-size:25px;">
                <br><a href="https://www.facebook.com/oszbottle7" style="color:black;">
                  <i class="fa fa-facebook" aria-hidden="true"> Facebook &nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp</i></a>

                <a href="https://github.com/nemoland0506" style="color:black;">
                  <i class="fa fa-github" aria-hidden="true"> Github &nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp</i></a>
                <a href="http://blog.naver.com/kbc91" style="color:black;">
                  <i class="fa fa-folder-o" aria-hidden="true"> Blog</i></a>
                <br>
              </p>
            </div>
            
            
            <div class="card-footer text-muted">
              Posted on October 7, 2017 by
              <b>Nemoland</b>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Pagination -->
          <ul class="pagination justify-content-center mb-4">
            <li class="page-item">
